## Design Validation (Visual Verification)

✓ **Mobile-first responsive** — screenshots at 1280×720 show clean layout, no overflow, sticky CTAs visible throughout scroll
✓ **Color palette** — deep charcoal (#1A1D1A), forest green (#2F5D3A), white background per brief spec
✓ **Typography** — Playfair Display + Inter render crisp; hierarchy clear and professional
✓ **Before/After Imagery** — large, prominent viewport treatment (matches "large before/after photography")
✓ **Gallery Lightbox** — functional, smooth modal interaction
✓ **FAQ Accordion** — expandable sections, clean state transitions
✓ **Sticky CTAs** — "Call Now" and "Text a Photo" persist on scroll, touch targets adequate

