- produced: 7 PNG hero-flow screenshots (1280×720, valid 8-bit RGB) + 1 muted WebM video (~90s, live demo); all verified against live endpoint.
- decisions: Kept desktop viewport (1280×720) for proposal clarity; video is muted (audio unnecessary for UX flow). Screenshots sequenced hero-to-footer for narrative coherence.
